{"tid":2509373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上訴庭指「裝修」等同私了 斥搶奪法官飯碗 (法律功能與地位)","createTime":"2021-04-29T11:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:04:20.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2492bbf35c24daa688643631bbc55ccdb37b28","tid":2509373,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"7.21白衣人無差別襲擊市民翌日，大批市民到立法會議員何君堯辦事處破壞。患有過度活躍的男學生事後承認刑事毀壞罪，原本被判感化，經律政司覆核後改判服務令。<span class=\"red\">惟律政司仍然不滿，向上訴庭申請覆核刑罰</span>，最終男生被判入教導所。上訴庭今頒下判刑理由，指原審裁判官嚴重誤判案情嚴重性及被告罪責，沒意識到本案涉及仇視、恐嚇及滅聲元素。而本案可歸類為「裝修」事件，本質上與「私了」無異，形容是<span class=\"red\">「搶奪法律的功能和地位，把個人眼中的對錯強加於人，並進行報復」。</span><br />\n<br />\n再加上<span class=\"red\">本案的反修例及白衣人事件背景，認為被告行為隨時引發更廣泛違法活動，增添案情嚴重性。</span><br />\n<br />\n最後，彭官質疑被告在證據確鑿的情況下，仍然堅稱他只是隨手拿起硬物加入打鬥，反映他缺乏深刻反省，認為他只是為求輕判才向何君堯道歉，「無論有幾多次（道歉），都不是出於真誠悔意」。"},{"pid":"f0045f1f27974c4ec301fa8eec4df99ca87f99e7","tid":2509373,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:24:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/FIM5B3334VADVCZ2FLUKJGACPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FFIM5B3334VADVCZ2FLUKJGACPQ%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=9500655e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FFIM5B3334VADVCZ2FLUKJGACPQ%2F&h=ea0e33d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/FIM5B3334VADVCZ2FLUKJGACPQ/</a>"},{"pid":"b31b52bf1a8b30f9a0542670dae18b63d95cb538","tid":2509373,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:27:07.000Z","msg":"匪官都驚人搶？"},{"pid":"11177c8b3716beee083dddd1dfebce63bbecbd49","tid":2509373,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"就係見到啲咁仆街既判訣決定唔打針"},{"pid":"19f42673a54d715fc6b09ed219c01f034def6de6","tid":2509373,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f27125a6c85167d4bd22e9fbcdcbe6499d15f7","tid":2509373,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"食屎啦加刑庭"},{"pid":"1021bca450b1b3fa57a61cefc88c167a301eaf5a","tid":2509373,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11177c8b3716beee083dddd1dfebce63bbecbd49","tid":2509373,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"就係見到啲咁仆街既判訣決定唔打針"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:23.000Z","msg":"態度正確"},{"pid":"29f9bd0d285f032c59eb930c18d8dbcc0232ce65","tid":2509373,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"納粹庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}